rComments: Teaches asynchrone with pre made videos, critoph did office hours and she was good too. This prof explains very clearly the content in her videos, you will understand. You can get a good grade with minimal effort but you have to do the homework because those mirror the mcq exams very closely.

I think this was her first year teaching and you can kinda tell. She seems to know what she's talking about but has trouble explaining it. She's very hard to follow and as she explains she's all over the place and kinda stutters on her words which made it hard to follow.

A very good teacher explains his course very well. Always available so that these students can succeed in their subject. Answers his emails very quickly. If you want to succeed, do his exercises and those in the book help a lot. Have study groups and you will succeed in his class. Do not hesitate to contact her.
